TextEng: "You be too old. You go home!"
"You are too old. Why not just go home?"
Text: 너무 늙으셨네요. 그냥 집에 가시는 게 어때요?

TextEng: "You help me by tell me 'bout Undermountain."
Text: 나한테 언더마운틴 얘기해 줘. 도움 돼.

TextEng: "You could help me by telling me about Undermountain."
Text: 언더마운틴에 대해 알려주시면 도움이 될 것 같아요.
나 항상 언더마운틴 예측 안 된다고 들었어.

TextEng: "I've always been told Undermountain is unpredictable."
"That stupid. Me was hoping for something me could use."
Text: 그거 바보 같아. 나 쓸모 있는 거 기대했는데.

TextEng: "That's stupid. I was hoping for something useful."
"Me like greedy. It make me wealthy."
Text: 나 탐욕 좋아. 부자 되게 해줘.

TextEng: "My greed has served me well so far."
"You aren't too old. Get down there and fight!"
Text: 너무 늙지 않으셨어요. 거기 가서 싸우세요!

TextEng: "Well, me tried. If you think you be too old, then you be so."
Text: 뭐, 나 해봤어. 네가 너무 늙었다 생각하면 그런 거지.

TextEng: "Well, I tried. If you think you're too old, then maybe you are."
Text: 뭐, 해봤네요. 본인이 너무 늙었다고 생각하면 그런 거겠죠.
